{"analytics_identifier":"D116","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-statistics-authority","content_id":"cd90918d-e15b-4d9a-939d-deabc465c824","description":"The UK Statistics Authority promotes and safeguards the production and publication of official statistics that serve the public good. It also promotes and safeguards the quality and comprehensiveness of official statistics, and ensures good practice in relation to official statistics using the Code of Practice for Statistics . Statistics is a non-ministerial department, supported by 1 public body .","details":{"acronym":"Statistics","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The UK Statistics Authority promotes and safeguards the production and publication of official statistics that serve the public good. It also promotes and safeguards the quality and comprehensiveness of official statistics, and ensures good practice in relation to official statistics using the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.statisticsauthority.gov.uk/code-of-practice/\">Code of Practice for Statistics</a>.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"UK Statistics Authority\">Statistics</abbr> is a non-ministerial department, supported by <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations#uk-statistics-authority\">1 public body</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":null,"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"UK Statistics Authority"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"http://www.statisticsauthority.gov.uk/"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"non_ministerial_department","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-01-11T14:32:57+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifi